Date: Sat, 4 Jul 2026 19:07:43 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 08/13] Add in-tree hardened_malloc backend
 (--with-malloc=hardened-malloc)

Vendor GrapheneOS hardened_malloc with wrapper sources for embed builds and
optional preload helper scripting.
